{
  "stem": "304.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I said, I am one of those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I'm not the only one because I was-- there were many departments.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I am not the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "A lot of us are doing that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I felt that I am doing the right thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then, one night-- and we had to-- the hardest thing was to work at night from 6:00 in the evening, 6:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because at night, you didn't receive any food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You had an hour, midnight, an hour break.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But what happened, daytime you went to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Lunchtime, you had an hour break.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You got-- the vegetable soup was much better and, and, and thicker and even had tiny pieces of meat in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So we received this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then when we went home, we received the evening meal, the bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You know, I never talked about it, piece of bread, a thin slice of salami, and a little square of margarine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "This was the ration.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was bigger and a little bit better than in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And if we succeeded to, to save a little piece of bread, we kept it for breakfast.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But if you work at night, you came home on empty stomach, you went to sleep-- home-- you came back to--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--camp.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they woke you up lunchtime to have the soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you got up, you had the soup, you went back to sleep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they woke you up to get your evening meal and to, to wash up and go to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you were so hungry you almost ate all the bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the whole night, you had to work 12 hours physically and no food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one day at night, I think I fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A sudden, I heard somebody tapping me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
